{"tid":865341,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"老豆講野好鍾意加“佢老母個閪”","createTime":"2018-10-17T03:46:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T11:34:19.000Z","uid":82710,"like":78,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"482a5eb07de7759d9f914a6de674476576356a08","tid":865341,"uid":82710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T03:46:10.000Z","msg":"老豆同朋友傾計，傾電話，乃至最近入醫院，講咩都加句&ldquo;佢老母個閪&rdquo;&ldquo;屌你啊媽&rdquo;。<br />\n係屋企講電話傾計大聲到全層聽到，唔緊要，你COPD 肺炎入到醫院，透唔到氣，你覺得d醫護係咁聽&ldquo;佢老母個閪&rdquo;會點？<br />\n呢一年教老豆用電話，用視像通話，就話&ldquo;佢老母個閪唔記得&rdquo;，聽一分鐘就唔肯學。<br />\n個人本身粗鄙冇問題，問題係個人態度同脾氣。<br />\n我拍拖咁耐都唔敢帶另一半返去，除左因為你講野真係好失禮好樣衰，係因為你自以為是既脾氣。"},{"pid":"7aab3012c3304af574bf1dccd4d55ec65574657e","tid":865341,"uid":137768,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T03:47:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我會改架啦"},{"pid":"8116c548b90078a983f4c912120699d419db2e08","tid":865341,"uid":82710,"like":87,"dislike":1,"score":86,"quote":{"pid":"7aab3012c3304af574bf1dccd4d55ec65574657e","tid":865341,"uid":137768,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T03:47:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我會改架啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T03:48:03.000Z","msg":"第一個留言竟然唔係&ldquo;佢老母個閪&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6c7567d074e04d540ffeea06eda9791bead891","tid":865341,"uid":25062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T03:48:12.000Z","msg":"係咪細唔缺乏母親關心"},{"pid":"268ae77d65ca7527ed09c4d1ffcd3e9a7db15227","tid":865341,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3a6c7567d074e04d540ffeea06eda9791bead891","tid":865341,"uid":25062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T03:48:12.000Z","msg":"係咪細唔缺乏母親關心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T03:49:29.000Z","msg":"細個越缺少大個就會越想要嗰樣嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji